
Installing
----------

$ ln -s /path/to/your/repo/vim ~/.vim
$ ln -s /path/to/your/repo/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Run these commands from the toplevel of the working tree.

$ git submodule init
$ git submodule update
$ git submodule foreach git submodule init
$ git submodule foreach git submodule update

Or just run install.sh

More info
---------

See http://sontek.net/turning-vim-into-a-modern-python-ide
